      "title": "The President leaves for Singapore",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Bangladeshi media reported that Sri Lankan President Gotabaya Rajapaksa and his entourage left a few moments ago on SV788 flight belonging to Saudi Airlines for Singapore.",
        "The Bangladeshi media mentioned that the flight SV 788 belonging to the Saudi Airlines is scheduled to land in Singapore at around 7 pm Singapore time."
